STATE of Connecticut
v.
Darnell WALKER Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided January 18, 2017

Jodi Zils Gagne, assigned counsel, in support of the petition.

Marjorie Allen Dauster, senior assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The defendant's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 169 Conn.App. 906, 150 A.3d 1191 (2016), is denied.
